
[1]slanderous

   SLA'NDEROUS, a.

   1. That utters defamatory words or tales; as a slanderous tongue.

   2. Containing slander or defamation; calumnious; as slanderous words,
   speeches or reports, false and maliciously uttered.

   3. Scandalous; reproachful.
